snippet.title: Project Terra Pre-Alpha Footage August 2022
snippet.description:
Just in time before Gamescom a little preview of how things are going with Project Terra.

Here you can see a new site to the world of the game: an hostile surrounding filled with aggressive creatures that will later transform back to a more natural state - but with enemies still in it?
